Among the most popular materials in the last five months are notes of the Kremlin's powerlessness in its relations with Ukraine, the death of a soloist of the group "King and Cock", pogroms in the capital city of Birulov.
The conflict between Rosbalt and Roskomnadzor began in July 2013, when the amendments to the media law came into force, prohibiting journalists from fighting uncensorship.
